https://github.com/jcfischer","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jcfischer/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jcfischer/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jcfischer/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jcfischer/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jcfischer/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jcfischer/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jcfischer/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jcfischer/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jcfischer/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-12-16t16:01:43z","updated_at":"2013-12-16t16:01:43z","body":"more data:\r\n\r\nafter the file has finished uploading (in chunks), i see that the apache process writes with around 400-500kb/s and the nfs server also writes with 400-500kb/s to disk. \r\n\r\nwriting a file directly from the web server machine to the nfs server (via dd to the mounted directorry) yields a throughput of around 20 mb/s (which seems reasonable). \r\n\r\nquestions:\r\n- why is apache writing so slowly? \r\n- why is it writing twice? (once during the actual upload, once afterwards?)\r\n- could this be due to the data being encrypted (owncloud encryption)?"},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/30740988","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/6443#issuecomment-30740988","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/6443","id":30740988,"user":{"login":"jcfischer","id":3088,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/5085ba37ba624a788e04a842cd09bd6e?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2fdc6a7e655d7e5840e66733e9ee67cc69.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"5085ba37ba624a788e04a842cd09bd6e","url":"https://api.github.com/users/jcfischer","html_url":"https://github.com/jcfischer","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jcfischer/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jcfischer/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jcfischer/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jcfischer/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jcfischer/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jcfischer/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jcfischer/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jcfischer/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jcfischer/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-12-17t10:40:58z","updated_at":"2013-12-17t10:40:58z","body":"we found the problems: \r\n\r\na) owncloud writes the files in 8kb blocks\r\nb) we had our nfs directory mounted with the \"sync\" option\r\n\r\nremounting with async increased the write speed immensly\r\n\r\n"},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/30741325","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/6443#issuecomment-30741325","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/6443","id":30741325,"user":{"login":"karlitschek","id":867445,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/87ce2b4531ee1a0c32b50e0d8f049224?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2f06e7098636caebfc9c30c9f52eb905df.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"87ce2b4531ee1a0c32b50e0d8f049224","url":"https://api.github.com/users/karlitschek","html_url":"https://github.com/karlitschek","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/karlitschek/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/karlitschek/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/karlitschek/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/karlitschek/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/karlitschek/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/karlitschek/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/karlitschek/repos","e